\": \"the ParalympicsGB squad\", \"from\": 875, \"to\": 898}]}, {\"sentence\": \"McGarry has come through a testing spell since the end of last year as he battled a white blood cell disease which \\\"absolutely ravaged\\\" him, the prescribed medication meaning he was a lot more suspectable to muscle tears.\", \"from\": 948, \"to\": 1169, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"McGarry\", \"from\": 948, \"to\": 955}, {\"ngram\": \"a testing spell\", \"from\": 973, \"to\": 988}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 995, \"to\": 1002}, {\"ngram\": \"last year\", \"from\": 1006, \"to\": 1015}, {\"ngram\": \"a white blood cell disease\", \"from\": 1030, \"to\": 1056}, {\"ngram\": \"the prescribed medication\", \"from\": 1089, \"to\": 1114}, {\"ngram\": \"muscle tears\", \"from\": 1156, \"to\": 1168}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Given his additional health issues, it looked very much as if McGarry would not be able to fulfil his Paralympic dream, before those impressive lifts of 231kg and 232kg put him back on course for Paris.\", \"from\": 1171, \"to\": 1373, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1367, \"end\": 1372, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999992570381468, \"rank\": 7.429623674189985e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his additional health issues\", \"from\": 1177, \"to\": 1205}, {\"ngram\": \"McGarry\", \"from\": 1233, \"to\": 1240}, {\"ngram\": \"his Paralympic dream\", \"from\": 1269, \"to\": 1289}, {\"ngram\": \"those impressive lifts\", \"from\": 1298, \"to\": 1320}, {\"ngram\": \"231kg\", \"from\": 1324, \"to\": 1329}, {\"ngram\": \"232kg\", \"from\": 1334, \"to\": 1339}, {\"ngram\": \"course\", \"from\": 1356, \"to\": 1362}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We got over the line, to a lot of people's surprise, so those two kilos for a personal best were probably the biggest two kilos I have ever found in my career,\\\" McGarry told the PA news agency.\", \"from\": 1375, \"to\": 1569, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the line\", \"from\": 1388, \"to\": 1396}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1401, \"to\": 1406}, {\"ngram\": \"people's surprise\", \"from\": 1410, \"to\": 1427}, {\"ngram\": \"those two kilos\", \"from\": 1432, \"to\": 1447}, {\"ngram\": \"the biggest two kilos\", \"from\": 1482, \"to\": 1503}, {\"ngram\": \"my career\", \"from\": 1525, \"to\": 1534}, {\"ngram\": \"McGarry\", \"from\": 1537, \"to\": 1544}, {\"ngram\": \"the PA news agency\", \"from\": 1550, \"to\": 1568}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It has been a far from an ideal run up into my first Games, but that is just more testament to my character and my belief.\", \"from\": 1571, \"to\": 1694, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an ideal run\", \"from\": 1595, \"to\": 1607}, {\"ngram\": \"my first Games\", \"from\": 1616, \"to\": 1630}, {\"ngram\": \"just more testament\", \"from\": 1644, \"to\": 1663}, {\"ngram\": \"my character\", \"from\": 1667, \"to\": 1679}, {\"ngram\": \"my belief\", \"from\": 1684, \"to\": 1693}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have made it to the Games, so now I sit here and say: 'why can not I go one step further?'\", \"from\": 1696, \"to\": 1789, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1715, \"to\": 1724}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Anything that is going to come across my path in Paris, I have already overcome much worse in tenfold - so now the delusional side of me has got his eyes on upsetting the medal party.\\\"\", \"from\": 1791, \"to\": 1976, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1841, \"end\": 1846, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999992570381468, \"rank\": 7.429623674189985e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my path\", \"from